{"tid":520710,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日去左入境助理體測","createTime":"2018-01-05T16:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T04:20:18.000Z","uid":53209,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3273aa722101c708ff674d1084cf3244fba7a4f7","tid":520710,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"跑到半殘 成功過到體測 之後到GROUP IN<br />\nIN既時候我組入面 有部份人係只係發言一次就停晒手腳, 甚至有人係去到十幾分鐘都唔講野<br />\n我開頭仲以為搶野講既情況會好激烈(咁當然都有)<br />\n但有部份人去到野都唔多講句  係貪跑800米跑到狗咁 同坐車入去好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"592d5a2b32a86d96e8b1b53d15b6da8d23062045","tid":520710,"uid":51105,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"入境個800好撚輕鬆<br />\n你唔好講出黎比人笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4800e6b0692823de2e0351192e2c0f6365b80e","tid":520710,"uid":2671,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:15:43.000Z","msg":"講一兩句一樣可以入到FIB，樓主係咪未知個遊戲點玩？"},{"pid":"a10cee5fc4fa9f8d516338481af7fc22e8bf05bc","tid":520710,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7e4800e6b0692823de2e0351192e2c0f6365b80e","tid":520710,"uid":2671,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:15:43.000Z","msg":"講一兩句一樣可以入到FIB，樓主係咪未知個遊戲點玩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T04:34:20.000Z","msg":"如果知點玩，唔講野都有OFFER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1018ea75697f62dc8859dc5ac3074244c7103bf","tid":520710,"uid":65030,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T04:37:35.000Z","msg":"樓主咁搶風頭有機會考官唔like,<br />\n散仔最緊要聽聽話話，唔駛咁醒，<br />\n咁醒會令考官覺得你英雄主義唔聽教"},{"pid":"6357d56e3cb1371c6cb6d330742208b4cc2f6dce","tid":520710,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1018ea75697f62dc8859dc5ac3074244c7103bf","tid":520710,"uid":65030,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"